    executiveSummary: "The cryptocurrency market is witnessing a significant shift with the rise of layer-2 scaling solutions, particularly on the Bitcoin and Ethereum networks. With a 300% growth in transactions in the last 6 months, Bitcoin L2s are revolutionizing the way we think about scalability and adoption. As regulatory clarity improves, institutional investment is expected to pour in, driving the growth of the L2 ecosystem.",
